Data details
File: Biomass.tif
Type: static raster (2020)
Resolution: 100 Ã— 100 m
Units: tons per hectare (t/ha)
Projection: EPSG 4326 (WGS 84)
Extent: Rectangle_Europe (pan-European coverage)

Use
Provides a harmonized baseline of forest biomass for assessing carbon stocks, 
harvest potential, and sustainable forest management strategies across Europe.
